name: HamburgerShop
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: hamburger shop
des:
Hamburger Shop is a skill that manages orders from order, preparation to delivery by number.

For each order, there is ID number. 
When take order, say for example, number 10 order. 
When food prepared, say for example, number 10 prepred. 
When food delivered, say for example, number 10 delete. 

In the screen attached device, a number list of “Order" and “Prepared" will be shown.
When you say remind, the list of “Order" and “Prepared" will be read out. 
When you say reset, a number list of order and prepared will be initialized.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
